trans-unit.source: Represents a Windows menu or toolbar command item.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et Windows-menyen eller verktøylinjen kommandoen-element.

trans-unit.source: The MenuCommand class represents information about a Windows menu or toolbar command.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuCommand representerer informasjon om en Windows-menyen eller verktøylinjen kommando.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> interface allows you to add MenuCommand objects to the Visual Studio menu.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>grensesnittet kan du legge til MenuCommand objekter i Visual Studio-menyen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>

trans-unit.source: This class provides the following members: - An event-handler property to which you can attach an event handler for the command.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen gir følgende medlemmer:-en hendelsesbehandlingen egenskap som du kan knytte en hendelsesbehandling for kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> property that uniquely identifies the command.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>-egenskap som identifiserer kommandoen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A> method that executes the command.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A>metode som kjører kommandoen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OnCommandChanged%2A> method that can be overridden to handle the event that occurs when a new command is selected.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OnCommandChanged%2A>metode som kan overstyres for å behandle hendelsen oppstår når en ny kommando er valgt.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OnCommandChanged%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Boolean flag states that indicate whether the command is <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Checked%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Enabled%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Supported%2A>, or <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -Boolsk flagg tilstander som viser om kommandoen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Checked%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Enabled%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Supported%2A>, eller <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible%2A>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Supported%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Enabled%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Checked%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OleStatus%2A> property that indicates the OLE command status code for the command.
trans-unit.target: – En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OleStatus%2A>egenskap som angir OLE kommando statuskode for kommandoen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.OleStatus%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An override for the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.ToString%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: -Overstyringer for den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.ToString%2A>metoden.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.ToString%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The event to raise when the user selects the menu item or toolbar button.
trans-unit.target: Hendelsen opphøye når brukeren velger menyknappen element eller verktøylinjen.

trans-unit.source: The unique command ID that links this menu command to the environment's menu.
trans-unit.target: Unike kommando-ID som denne kommandoen er koblet til det miljøet-menyen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether this menu item is checked.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om det er merket av for dette alternativet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item is checked; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet er sjekket; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the menu command changes.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når kommandoen endres.

trans-unit.source: A command can change if it becomes checked or disabled.
trans-unit.target: En kommando kan endre hvis den blir merket eller deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> associated with this menu command.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"> </xref> som er forbundet med denne kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> associated with the menu command.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"> </xref> knyttet til kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether this menu item is available.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om dette alternativet er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item is enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet er aktivert. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Invokes the command.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: Invokes the command with the given parameter.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer kommandoen med den angitte parameteren.

trans-unit.source: An optional argument for use by the command.
trans-unit.target: Et valgfritt argument for bruk av kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the OLE command status code for this menu item.
trans-unit.target: Henter statuskoden OLE kommandoen for dette menyelementet.

trans-unit.source: An integer containing a mixture of status flags that reflect the state of this menu item.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som inneholder en blanding av status som gjenspeiler statusen for dette alternativet.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.CommandChanged"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Hever den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.CommandChanged"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: Raising an event invokes the event handler through a delegate.
trans-unit.target: Opprettet en hendelse aktiverer hendelsesbehandlingen via en representant.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [NIB: Raising an Event](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f2adaf01-1ed1-42e1-8c31-8d467e7e0ee2).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [NIB: opprettet en hendelse](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f2adaf01-1ed1-42e1-8c31-8d467e7e0ee2).

trans-unit.source: The OnCommandChanged method also allows derived classes to handle the event without attaching a delegate.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnCommandChanged kan også avledede klasser behandle hendelsen uten å knytte representant.

trans-unit.source: This is the preferred technique for handling the event in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er den foretrukne metoden for behandling av hendelsen i en avledet klasse.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.EventArgs> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.EventArgs>som inneholder Hendelsesdata.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Gets the public properties associated with the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter felles egenskaper som er tilknyttet den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: All menu commands store their public properties in the Properties collection.
trans-unit.target: Alle kommandoer lagre offentlige egenskapene i Egenskaper-samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The key in the properties dictionary is the property name.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen i Egenskaper-ordlisten er navnet på egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: This allows for generic enumeration of properties and provides a consistent substrate from which new properties can be added without modifying the class definition.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig for generell opplisting av egenskapene og gir en konsekvent banen nye egenskaper som kan legges uten å endre klassedefinisjonen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> containing the public properties of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>som inneholder egenskapene fellesnøkkel for den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether this menu item is supported.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dette alternativet støttes.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item is supported, which is the default; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet støttes, er standard. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representation of this menu command.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en strengrepresentasjon av denne kommandoen.

trans-unit.source: A string containing the value of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.CommandID*> property appended with the names of any flags that are set, separated by pipe bars (|). These flag properties include <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Checked*>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Enabled*>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Supported*>, and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible*>.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder verdien for den <> </> *> egenskapen legges til navnene på alle flaggene som er angitt, atskilt med datakanalen stolper |. Egenskapene flagget omfatter <> </> *>, <> </> *>, <> </> *>, og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible*>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Visible*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether this menu item is visible.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om dette alternativet er synlig.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item is visible; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet er synlige. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
